WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:02.733
Why did you fire me

2
00:00:02.733 --> 00:00:03.533
Jiang Yan

3
00:00:03.966 --> 00:00:05.800
Is your brain broken?

4
00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:08.400
Manager Bai is the day of our textile factory

5
00:00:08.466 --> 00:00:11.333
Who does he want to fire without a reason?

6
00:00:11.333 --> 00:00:13.733
I'm more reasonable

7
00:00:13.733 --> 00:00:16.100
There was a reason for firing him

8
00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:17.233
What reason can you have?

9
00:00:17.333 --> 00:00:19.466
Your firing me is nothing more than public revenge

10
00:00:19.466 --> 00:00:21.066
Your husband is a gambler

11
00:00:21.066 --> 00:00:22.966
It is easy to damage the reputation of our factory.

12
00:00:22.966 --> 00:00:24.666
You disobey factory management

13
00:00:24.733 --> 00:00:27.666
How can I manage others if I don't punish you severely

14
00:00:27.933 --> 00:00:30.700
I order you to get out of the textile factory now

15
00:00:30.766 --> 00:00:32.200
Let you die

16
00:00:32.333 --> 00:00:35.400
Originally, it was just a little year-end benefit.

17
00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:37.366
Don't make trouble to the point of being fired

18
00:00:37.366 --> 00:00:38.733
Now you are satisfied

19
00:00:38.733 --> 00:00:39.533
OK

20
00:00:40.133 --> 00:00:41.900
I go stop

21
00:00:41.933 --> 00:00:43.300
You missed a day's work

22
00:00:43.300 --> 00:00:44.733
Caused damage to the factory

23
00:00:44.733 --> 00:00:47.633
You need to compensate another 200 yuan to go to the white belt country.

24
00:00:47.933 --> 00:00:49.333
Are you being unreasonable?

25
00:00:49.333 --> 00:00:51.466
Jiang Yan, what are you?

26
00:00:51.466 --> 00:00:52.966
Dare to call Manager Bai by his first name

27
00:00:52.966 --> 00:00:56.166
You really think you are the factory manager, you are right

28
00:00:57.100 --> 00:00:59.400
My wife is the director of this factory

